                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/1851</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-06-04T16:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 4, 1916, 4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In view of the probable insistence of the Senate to meet to-morrow and proceed
                    with election Henríquez, Council of Ministers has decided to arrest and imprison
                    four of the Arias Senators to-night. This will probably bring about trouble in
                    the city.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
